  "title": "Debt Recovery Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>TKQP Law LLP is a respected law firm located in the CBD area.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join TKQP Law LLP as a Debt Recovery Officer within our Banking Litigation Department, contributing to effective debt recovery processes and supporting the firm’s commitment to legal excellence.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage and execute debt recovery activities to support the Banking Litigation Department’s objectives</li><li>Collaborate with legal and administrative teams to ensure timely resolution of debt recovery cases</li><li>Pay attention to case details and documentation</li><li>Communicate effectively with clients to facilitate debt recovery processes</li><li>Maintain accurate records and reports to track progress </li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office</li></ul>",
